<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:48:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>参议员关注具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行和加密货币支持者发生争执</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</link><description>随着参议院一个重要小组开始考虑一项具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行集团正在最后一刻对稳定币收益率进行妥协。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWhBANxj4P6o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 23:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</guid></item><item><title>加密行业在熊市中举办脱衣舞派对</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/crypto-industry-throws-lap-dance-party-in-middle-of-bear-market</link><description>周三晚上，人们排着几个街区的队，等待了几个小时才进入迈阿密的 E11even 俱乐部，几个男人兴奋地谈论着他们计划进入的膝上舞。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i79v8LGzeGTc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/crypto-industry-throws-lap-dance-party-in-middle-of-bear-market</guid></item><item><title>贝莱德准备推出两只代币化货币市场基金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-08/blackrock-readies-launch-of-two-tokenized-money-market-funds</link><description>贝莱德公司(BlackRock Inc.)计划推出两只货币市场基金，专为将现金存放在稳定币而非银行账户的投资者而设立，这表明这家全球最大的资产管理公司看到了数字美元经济中持久的客户群。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/il9lg0ZDzPqQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 21:18:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-08/blackrock-readies-launch-of-two-tokenized-money-market-funds</guid></item></channel></rss>